  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个云原生部署的流程图。起点是K8s集群，然后要接入服务网格，最后通过Helm Chart完成应用分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，K8s集群作为入口。那服务网格这部分需要体现什么细节吗？是单向流转还是有分支判断？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务网格这里有个关键点：资源到位后要做一个决策节点，根据策略分成三条路径——One、Two、或者Three。前两条还是走服务网格内部，第三条才落到Helm Chart。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：K8s集群 → 服务网格（带'Get money'的触发条件）→ 决策节点 → 三条分支。其中'Three'分支指向Helm Chart，One和Two留在服务网格内。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但决策节点本身也是服务网格的状态，只是需要菱形表示。另外'Get money'这个触发条件要标注在第一条连线上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：K8s集群方框，带'Get money'的箭头指向服务网格方框，然后服务网格分出菱形决策节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，决策节点之后的三条分支，One和Two虽然留在服务网格，但应该是不同的服务网格实例或者状态，需要区分开。Helm Chart是最终部署动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整：决策节点分出三条标注线——'One'和'Two'分别指向两个独立的服务网格节点，'Three'指向Helm Chart节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题，决策节点C和前面的服务网格B重复了，C应该是菱形判断而不是再用方框。而且B到C的连线不需要额外标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修复完成：B保持为服务网格方框，C改为菱形决策节点，B到C是无标注连线。三条分支从C引出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看一眼D和E，这两个服务网格节点——虽然类型相同，但在图中需要作为独立节点存在，名称可以一样。F的Helm Chart要明显区分出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "最终结构确认：A(K8s集群) --Get money-- B(服务网格) -- C{决策} --One-- D(服务网格), --Two-- E(服务网格), --Three-- F(Helm Chart)。所有节点类型和标注都符合要求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流程准确反映了我们的云原生部署策略。可以定稿了。",
